Rule Learning, Probabilistic Methods. 

Rule Learning is present in the text as the paper discusses the use of Reduced Error Pruning in relational learning algorithms, which are a type of rule learning algorithm. 

Probabilistic Methods are also present in the text as the paper proposes a new method, Incremental Reduced Error Pruning, which attempts to address the problems with Reduced Error Pruning. This new method involves using probabilistic methods to incrementally update the decision tree.
